                            <comment id="12920579" author="markrmiller@gmail.com" created="Wed, 13 Oct 2010 14:23:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Probably more to come here - but this patch adds writing out the defaultCoreName to the persist method, and adds a test for this.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12922951" author="markrmiller@gmail.com" created="Wed, 20 Oct 2010 13:25:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m still looking to see if there are more problems here, but I have committed the issue covered in the current patch - that is/was a clear and simple to address bug. I just want to make sure there is not another part to this before resolving.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12924347" author="ephraimofir" created="Sun, 24 Oct 2010 16:25:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed indentation of solr.xml when serializing and added to CHANGES.txt&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
